able gates per ADR-2605261330. 4 constitutional firsts (G7, G8, G12, G14). Changes require Council Lv6+ supermajority + new ADR.", "gates" {"G7" "CONSTITUTIONAL FIRST: ABS MANDATORY on all 4-stroke ≥125cc and all electric ≥6kW; no ABS-delete, no track-only carve-out, no cost-down strip; dual-channel hydraulic safety-redundant. Elevates EU 168/2013 Annex II to constitutional invariant. §1.13 adherent safety non-negotiable.", "G13" "Cross-actor circular feed — VIN pre-registered with hodoki at production; ≥10% recycled-content by mass via kanayama-via-hodoki by R3; battery cells for electric models from hikari R2+ second-life (SoH ≥85%).", "G11" "KPI caps R0–R1: ≤250cc gasoline OR ≤15kW electric; curb mass ≤200kg; cargo ≤30kg panniers. ≥500cc / >15kW / racing-spec = N2/N3 Wave 2 ADR.", "G9" "Inference paths (defect, paint, dyno, weld-vision) use Murakumo no-VKE mesh only", "G10" "Hot work + brake assembly + paint booth + battery handling SBT-gated personnel", "G5" "Paint artwork + decals pass Charter Rider §2(a-h) scan (no military / licensed-IP / addictive-thrill / racing-glorification)", "G6" "Sound emissions ≤80 dB @ 7.5m (UN-ECE R41); no aftermarket loud-exhaust enablement", "G8" "CONSTITUTIONAL FIRST: NO GPS tracker / NO connected-app / NO always-on telematics / NO V2X built-in / NO proprietary diagnostic-DRM. Only passive odometer + safety ECU + optional user-installed-after-purchase open-source GPS module. §2(c) anti-surveillance at vehicle BUILD time; companion to hodoki G8 (EOL data destroy) — closes surveillance loop across full lifecycle.", "G1" "All CAD (frame, body, fixture) + firmware (ECU, ABS, BMS) + tool fixtures open-source (Apache 2.0 + Charter Rider)", "G3" "Every critical step (frame weld, engine torque, brake torque) signed by witness quorum ≥2 distinct robots (ADR-2605191524)", "G4" "All owner + service manuals + safety labels + parts catalog JP + EN bilingual minimum", "G2" "Mass-balance ≥98% closure on kotoba-datomic; inherits kanayama + hodoki G2 cross-cell invariant pattern", "G14" "CONSTITUTIONAL FIRST: 30-YEAR MINIMUM design service life — frame + engine + transmission + motor + structural suspension designed for 30yr fatigue/corrosion/wear; mandatory parts availability 30yr post-discontinue; planned obsolescence prohibited; firmware 30yr update commitment. §1.13 wellbecoming applied to durable goods.", "G12" "CONSTITUTIONAL FIRST: RIGHT-TO-REPAIR FORWARD-PUBLISHING — every new vehicle ships with IPFS-pinned full parts catalog + CAD + firmware source + service manual + open diagnostic protocol; no proprietary lock-in; no anti-DRM; no warranty void on user repair; part discontinuation prohibited 30 years post-launch. §2(e) at build; companion to hodoki G12 (EOL catalog)."}}, "tier" "Tier-B", "@type" "ActorManifest", "nonGoals" {"description" "10 explicitly excluded scopes (constitutional N1–N10, immutable R0–R3)", "goals" {"N1" "Military motorcycles / armed motorcycle scout / weapon-mount-equipped. §2(a) constitutional.", "N6" "Trikes / sidecars / ATVs / quad / UTV. Separate Wave (different stability + regulatory class).", "N3" "Racing-focus / track-only / unlimited-class supersport. §1.13 anti-thrill-addictive + §2(e) anti-gatekeeping.", "N10" "Surveillance-tier touring (passenger camera / V2V always-on / pillion data collection). §2(c) + G8.", "N4" "Premium / luxury positioning / licensed-IP co-branding. §2(b) IP-encumbrance + §2(e) anti-tier-pricing.", "N7" "Pure human-powered bicycles / pedal-assist e-bikes. Wave 2 (different industrial scope + EPAC regulation).", "N2" "≥500cc displacement / sport-tourer / supersport / cruiser ≥1000cc. Wave 2 ADR + Council Lv6+ supermajority; premium/luxury class boundary.", "N8" "Aftermarket loud-exhaust enablement / 'performance' mods violating G6 or G7. No street-illegal-mod tolerance.", "N5" "Connected-app / always-on telematics / GPS tracker / V2X built-in / paired-phone / cloud-ECU. §2(c) + G8 constitutional first.", "N9" "Hydrogen fuel-cell motorcycles. Wave 2 ADR with dedicated thermal + pressure safety review."}}, "description" "Small-displacement motorcycle manufacturing Tier-B actor for adherent personal mobility. Adopts mature global motorcycle OEM methodology (frame → drivetrain → harness/suspension/paint → final → dyno); religious-corp-ised by 4 constitutional firsts: G7 ABS-mandatory ≥125cc / ≥6kW electric (safety constitutional), G8 build-time anti-surveillance (NO GPS / connected-app / telematics / V2X built-in; companion to hodoki G8 EOL data destroy), G12 right-to-repair forward-publishing (IPFS-pinned parts catalog + CAD + firmware source at manufacture; companion to hodoki G12 EOL catalog), G14 30-year design service life (anti-planned-obsolescence). R0 scope = ≤250cc 4-stroke single OR ≤15kW electric / curb ≤200kg / commuter+utility. ≥500cc, racing, luxury, connected-app surveillance, trikes/sidecars, pure bicycles, H2 FCV are constitutional non-goals."}}
